'''2008年巴基斯坦地震'''指[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[俾路支省|俾路支省]]发生的一次里氏6.4级的[[地震|地震]]，地震发生于2008年10月29日。[[美国地质调查局|美国地质调查局]]报告称，此次地震震中位于[[奎达|奎达]]北部{{convert|60|km|mi|abbr=on}}，距[[阿富汗|阿富汗]][[坎大哈|坎大哈]]{{convert|185|km|mi|abbr=on}}。地震发生于当地时间04:09（[[UTC|UTC]]时间10月28日23:09），震源深度{{convert|15|km|mi|abbr=on}}，坐标30.653°N, 67.323°E。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2008yscs.php|title=Magnitude 6.4 - PAKISTAN|date=October 28, 2008|publisher=USGS|accessdate=2008-10-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081102163545/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2008yscs.php|archivedate=2008-11-02}}</ref> 地震发生前12小时左右，在30.546°N, 67.447°E处发生了一次震源深度为{{convert|10|km|mi|abbr=on}}的里氏6.4级地震。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2008ytbk.php|title=Magnitude 6.4 - PAKISTAN|date=October 29, 2008|publisher=USGS|accessdate=2008-10-30|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081102163550/http://earthquake.usgs.gov/eqcenter/recenteqsww/Quakes/us2008ytbk.php|archivedate=2008-11-02}}</ref>地震造成215人死亡，超过200人受伤，<ref name=AFP /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601087&sid=aJUWhKXHlLTI&refer=home |title=Pakistan Earthquake Kills 150 People Near Quetta (Update1) |publisher=Bloomberg.com |date=2008-10-29 |accessdate=2008-10-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081116003829/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601087 |archivedate=2008-11-16 }}</ref><ref name=BBC>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/7696639.stm|title=Scores dead after Pakistan quake|publisher=BBC|date=2008-10-29|accessdate=2008-10-20|archive-date=2018-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226143720/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/7696639.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>120,000人无家可归。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/World-News/Pakistan-Earthquake-Near-Afghanistan-Border-Number-Of-Dead-Rising/Article/200810415131565?lpos=World_News_Top_Stories_Header_4&lid=ARTICLE_15131565_Pakistan_Earthquake_Near_Afghanistan_Border%2C_Number_Of_Dead_Rising |title=Pakistan Earthquake Near Afghanistan Border, Number Of Dead Rising |publisher=Sky News |date=2008-10-09 |accessdate=2008-10-30 |archive-date=2019-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822003902/https://news.sky.com/?lpos=World_News_Top_Stories_Header_4&lid=ARTICLE_15131565_Pakistan_Earthquake_Near_Afghanistan_Border,_Number_Of_Dead_Rising |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://africa.reuters.com/world/news/usnTRE49S261.html |title=Pakistan quake rescuers recover 160 bodies |publisher=Reuters.com |date=2008-10-29 |accessdate=2008-10-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=http://archive.wikiwix.com/cache/20081101114353/http://africa.reuters.com/world/news/usnTRE49S261.html |archivedate=2008-11-01 }}</ref>

